<SPAN CLASS="gutter">   3:</SPAN>    <SPAN CLASS="syntax18">&lt;</SPAN> Program continues here <SPAN CLASS="syntax18">&gt;</SPAN>
<SPAN CLASS="gutter">   4:</SPAN>    <SPAN CLASS="syntax8">while</SPAN>(<SPAN CLASS="syntax5">1</SPAN>)<SPAN CLASS="syntax18">{</SPAN>
